headline: Capital One Financial Corporation to Webcast Conference Call on Third Quarter 2025 Earnings
summary: MCLEAN, Va., September 26, 2025--On Tuesday, October 21, 2025, at approximately 4:05 p.m. Eastern Time, Capital One Financial Corporation (NYSE: COF) will release its third quarter 2025 earnings results. Additionally, the company will host a conference call at 5:00 p.m. Eastern Time to review financial and operating performance for the quarter ending September 30, 2025.

headline: Amex, Chase, Capital One: Which has the best travel credit card?
summary: Premium travel card fees are in focus after the Chase (JPM) Sapphire Reserve credit card's annual fee recently increased to $795, while American Express (AXP) refreshed its Amex Platinum card. Yahoo Finance Personal Finance Reporter Ben Walker joins Mind Your Money host Allie Canal to discuss whether the new Amex Platinum benefits are worth the hefty fees, and how the card compares to the Chase Sapphire Reserve and the Capital One (COF) Venture X card. Read more: Benefits of the new Amex Platinum card: Is the annual fee worth it?
